                <code>java.method.removed</code>
                <old>method java.util.Collection&lt;org.xwiki.contrib.activitypub.entities.AbstractActivity&gt; org.xwiki.contrib.activitypub.entities.Inbox::getAllActivities()</old>
                <justification>Young API: this method was wrong, you should rely on AbstractCollection methods.</justification>
              </item>
