                <justification>Young API and not a breakage.</justification>
              </item>
              <item>
                <code>java.method.parameterTypeChanged</code>
                <old>parameter &lt;O extends org.xwiki.contrib.activitypub.entities.AbstractCollection&lt;T&gt;&gt; O org.xwiki.contrib.activitypub.entities.OrderedCollection&lt;T extends org.xwiki.contrib.activitypub.entities.ActivityPubObject&gt;::addItem(===T===) @ org.xwiki.contrib.activitypub.entities.Outbox</old>
